	       been reported
             on the bug list. In __findenv, made string comparison "case
             insensitive" for Win32. On some systems (like mine) the
	     PATH variable
             name is actually "Path", so the cache dir was never
	     prepended to
             "Path". Found while fixing the bug in mktmpdir.c
